    <main id="main-content">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="issue-hero" style="background-image: url('assets/images/placeholder-hero.jpg');">
            <div class="issue-hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-hero-content">
                    <h1>Office of Science and Technology Policy</h1>
                    <p class="issue-hero-description">Advancing scientific discovery and technological innovation to create a brighter, more fabulous future for all dolls.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <section class="issue-overview-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="issue-overview-content">
                    <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
                    <p>The Office of Science and Technology Policy (OSTP) advises the President and others within the Executive Office on the effects of science and technology on domestic and international affairs. OSTP leads interagency efforts to develop and implement sound science and technology policies and budgets.</p>
                    <p>We work to ensure that the policies of the Executive Branch are informed by sound science, and that the scientific and technical work of the Executive Branch is properly coordinated to provide the greatest benefit to society. From dream technology to sustainable innovation, OSTP helps shape America's scientific enterprise.</p>
                    <p>Our office plays a crucial role in promoting STEM education, supporting research and development, addressing emerging technologies, and ensuring that scientific advancement benefits all doll communities equitably.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Key Initiatives -->
        <section class="initiatives-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Key Focus Areas</h2>
                <div class="initiatives-grid">
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🔬</span>
                        <h3>Scientific Research</h3>
                        <p>Supporting groundbreaking research across disciplines to solve challenges and improve quality of life for all dolls.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🚀</span>
                        <h3>Dream Technology</h3>
                        <p>Advancing innovative technologies that transform how dolls live, work, and pursue their dreams in the modern age.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🎓</span>
                        <h3>STEM Education</h3>
                        <p>Promoting science, technology, engineering, and mathematics education to prepare the next generation of doll innovators.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🤖</span>
                        <h3>Artificial Intelligence</h3>
                        <p>Ensuring AI development is ethical, equitable, and beneficial to all dolls while addressing potential risks.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">🌐</span>
                        <h3>Digital Infrastructure</h3>
                        <p>Building robust broadband and digital networks to connect every doll community to opportunity and innovation.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="initiative-card">
                        <span class="initiative-icon">⚡</span>
                        <h3>Clean Energy Innovation</h3>
                        <p>Developing breakthrough clean energy technologies to power dreamhouses sustainably and combat climate change.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Leadership Section -->
        <section class="priority-areas-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Leadership</h2>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>Director of OSTP & Science Advisor</h3>
                    <p>The Director of the Office of Science and Technology Policy serves as the President's Science Advisor and manages OSTP staff and policy development. This role requires Senate confirmation and involves coordinating research and development strategies across the federal government.</p>
                    <p>Working with leading scientists, engineers, and policy experts, the Director ensures that scientific integrity guides decision-making and that federal investments in research and development yield maximum benefit for doll society.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="priority-block">
                    <h3>National Science and Technology Council</h3>
                    <p>OSTP oversees the National Science and Technology Council (NSTC), the principal means for the President to coordinate science and technology policies across federal research and development programs. The NSTC brings together Cabinet members and agency heads to ensure federal science and technology initiatives are coordinated, collaborative, and effective.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

